## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for job.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers job visibility,
role-aware display,
duty/authority-aware surfaces,
historical job reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- job identity must resolve
- holder/assigning basis must resolve
- duty/authority scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid job identity
- invalid assignment basis
- invalid duty/authority scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish job state,
assignment scope,
authority scope,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- job runtime scope is explicit
- authority-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
